gw.api.domain.account

Interface AccountFinder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccountFinderImpl

    public interface AccountFinder
    Finder object for searching for Account entities in the local database by various criteria.
    See Also:
    PCDependencies.getAccountFinder

        Find an account matching a given publicId

      • findAccountByAccountNumber

        Account findAccountByAccountNumber(java.lang.String number)
        Returns the Account in the local database whose account number is number, or null if there is no such account. The search is case sensitive.
        Parameters:
        number - account number to be matched
        Returns:
        the matching account or null if none matches

      • findAccountSummaryByAccountNumber

        AccountSummary findAccountSummaryByAccountNumber(java.lang.String number)
        Returns the AccountSummary of the account in the local database whose account number is number, or null if there is no such account. The search is case sensitive.
        Parameters:
        number - the account number to be matched
        Returns:
        account summary for the given account or null if none matches

      • findAccountsByAccountNumbers

        Account[] findAccountsByAccountNumbers(java.lang.String[] numbers)
        Returns the Accounts in the database whose account numbers are in numbers.
        Parameters:
        numbers - account numbers against which the "AccountNumber" column of the Account table will be matched.
        Returns:
        An array containing matched accounts. The result is guaranteed to be non-null and to have the same length as numbers, but elements of the result will be null if no account exists with the corresponding number.

      • findAccountsStartingWithPrefix

        IQueryBeanResult<Account> findAccountsStartingWithPrefix(java.lang.String prefix)
        Returns an IQueryBeanResult containing all Accounts in the local database whose account number starts with prefix. The search is case insensitive.
        Parameters:
        prefix - account prefix to be partially matched
        Returns:
        accounts starting with the given prefix

      • findAccountSummariesForUser

        IQueryBeanResult<AccountSummary> findAccountSummariesForUser(User user)
        Returns an IQueryBeanResult of Accounts that are assigned to the given user.
        Parameters:
        user - the user to be matched
        Returns:
        query results containing matching account summaries
